description:
LibriVox recording of Märchen der Brüder Grimm by Jacob & Wilhelm Grimm. Read in German by Hans Hafen. Eine Auswahl der schönsten Märchen der Brüder Grimm. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
